The paper proposes a method for image dehazing using a fully convolutional neural network, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The method is agnostic to the atmosphere scattering model, which suggests that it may also fall under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The use of neural networks also suggests that it may fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. The paper also deals with image processing, which may fall under the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category. Finally, the paper proposes a method for improving image quality, which may fall under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
